{"tid":2046012,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"芝加哥示威者包圍特朗普大樓 扯美國旗扔落河","createTime":"2020-06-01T06:48:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T07:19:16.000Z","uid":70063,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"510ca6eae13d788eeed013d35a7807fe5b9d772d","tid":2046012,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:48:07.000Z","msg":"美國明尼蘇達州黑人弗洛伊德遭白人警員跪頸致死案，引爆全美多地連日示威。網傳影片可見，上周六（30日）芝加哥一批示威者包圍當地的特朗普大樓，期間更和到場的警員大打出手；期間有人將大樓門口一面美國國旗扔進河中。<br />\n<br />\n影片中，示威者把特朗普大樓門外的一面美國國旗取下，圍觀者中有大叫「燒了它」，另有人喊「扔到河裏」。隨後，一名黑衣男子將該面美國國旗扔到河中，圍觀群眾隨即歡呼和報以掌聲。另有影片顯示，示威者與前來維持秩序的警員爆發衝突，部分人更跳上警車，場面混亂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200531/mobile/bkn-20200531191602121-0531_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20200531%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200531191602121-0531_00972_001.html&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8wg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=c77ebff7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200531/mobile/bkn-20200531191602121-0531_00972_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9ec2b37cb4b0ca7da5794c3c9d9eb0456e1b9d44","tid":2046012,"uid":54884,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:50:20.000Z","msg":"好合理"},{"pid":"a765fb86f8dcdb93161868b900de5a88e896dbb8","tid":2046012,"uid":247845,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:54:20.000Z","msg":"佢哋反美定反侵？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67de91064b8c3981348dc5292bc5b8c37a38432b","tid":2046012,"uid":3241,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:56:31.000Z","msg":"香港屌下枝支那旗就又坐監又毒打<br />\n自由真好"},{"pid":"0dc4ba796eabd4bf760e2d3fbbb544e110139c43","tid":2046012,"uid":72749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a765fb86f8dcdb93161868b900de5a88e896dbb8","tid":2046012,"uid":247845,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:54:20.000Z","msg":"佢哋反美定反侵？ <img src=\"/